Package: drmTMB
Title: Distributional Regression Models Using Template Model Builder
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("drmTMB", "contributors", email = "maintainer@example.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
  )
Description: Fast distributional regression models for univariate and
    bivariate responses using Template Model Builder. The package is designed
    around formulae for distributional parameters such as location, scale,
    shape, zero inflation, random-effect scale, and residual correlation.
License: GPL (>= 3)
URL: https://itchyshin.github.io/drmTMB/, https://github.com/itchyshin/drmTMB
BugReports: https://github.com/itchyshin/drmTMB/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1.0)
